      Setting up the (Linux) rsync distribution
      =========================================

## $Id$    Frank Lübeck


(1) Choose a directory RSDIR and adjust the paths in 'rsyncd.conf' 
    (search 'export3')

(2) cd to RSDIR
    mkdir gap4
    
(3) copy the archives gap4r4.tar.gz, tools4r4.tar.gz, xtom1r1.tar.gz and
    packages-*.tar.gz to RSDIR/gap4

(4) copy 'gapsync/InstForRsync' to RSDIR/gap4 and start it

(5) copy the whole 'gapsync' directory to RSDIR/gap4/gap4r4 and move
    the file 'colorprompt.g' in RSDIR/gap4/gap4r4/lib

(6) start the server with 'startrsyncserver'

(7) That's it.

(8) For adjustments/improvements: edit scripts gapsync/InstForRsync
    and gapsync/gapsync and repeat steps (4) to (6) 
    
